{"tid":2012380,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"何君堯荃灣議辦收可疑物 爆炸品處理課一度戒備","createTime":"2020-05-11T14:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T16:49:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9feaf9143c8622332b86833e75cd67cfb064b2d6","tid":2012380,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:46:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200511/IFXZHYHQVQOQQ6VL7LMORTJJTM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200511%2FIFXZHYHQVQOQQ6VL7LMORTJJTM%2F&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=8dee887f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200511%2FIFXZHYHQVQOQQ6VL7LMORTJJTM%2F&h=8aeb20dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200511/IFXZHYHQVQOQQ6VL7LMORTJJTM/</a><br />\n<br />\n下午5時許，立法會議員何君堯位於荃灣荃豐中心的議員辦事處懷疑收到可疑物品，大批警員接報後封鎖現場調查，消防和爆炸品處理課亦到場戒備。至晚上可疑物品被撿走後，警方解除封鎖範圍，議辦則暫停開放，現場恢復平靜。"},{"pid":"76dc1c94a804581d2b4ccaef89d6bb3e5bb6e92d","tid":2012380,"uid":125502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"fce1b4264312ac652070be2bc2ee590b103b70da","tid":2012380,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\